personCountrySearchParameter

Parameter address-country:string

Searches based on the person's recorded country of address eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Person?address-country={country}

ResourcePerson
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPerson
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
